df %>% 
  filter(followersCount > friendsCount) %>%
  mutate(farklar = followersCount - friendsCount) %>%
  select(farklar) %>%
  summarise(n = n(),
            mean = mean(farklar),
            median = mean(farklar),
            sd = sd(farklar))

  filter(followersCount > friendsCount) %>%

  mutate(popi_indeksi = friendsCount / followersCount) %>%
